description:
Today we experiment combining TNT minecarts with the auto crafter to make some useful mining techniques. We delve into moss madness by making an 18 cell farm. We check out Joel's new Etho statues. Then we join up with BdoubleO to get some raid ravagers for the Frogger game replica.

Hermitcraft Website: http://www.hermitcraft.com
